      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in exemplary condition, having been preserved with meticulous attention to detail. Every surface reflects a standard of care that defies its age, offering an acquisition opportunity for the most discerning collector. Mechanical integrity is absolute, and the aesthetic presentation is flawless. We invite you to experience a vehicle that sets the definitive standard for its class.",
